description: Clearance of the existing site with redevelopment to create Co-living accommodation comprising of 264 rooms (Sui Generis), 1,258 sqm of communal multi use space, 157sqm of external terrace areas, with building heights between 2 and 8 storeys; with associated blue badge parking and cycle parking, hard and soft landscaping and public realm enhancements. (Demolition of the existing building)
